main_body:
Each year producers or producer groups shall transmit to the intervention agency of the Member State in which their holding is located or any other body designated by that Member State:
(a) before 15 October, a declaration of stocks held on 31 August, distinguishing between the types of rice defined in paragraph 2 of Annex A to Regulation (EC) No 3072/95 and specifying for each type the quantity held and the whole-grain yield;
(b) before 15 November, a crop declaration distinguishing between the types of rice defined in paragraph 2 of Annex A to Regulation (EC) No 3072/95 and specifying for each type the surface area used and the quantity of rice obtained.
